{"tid":1250393,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[新開㗎！] 96-00 TG 垃圾谷！","createTime":"2019-06-22T05:15:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T12:21:31.000Z","uid":2179,"like":1,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2a3362c1aaf6d20ee07f4536891ea9420dfdca92","tid":1250393,"uid":2179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:15:10.000Z","msg":"hi 各位96~00後嘅巴絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本人開新咗個TG谷 for 96~00後<br />\n其實係唔想有咁大代溝<br />\n如果你係玩抖音嘅00後就唔洗填了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地會不時就搞谷聚<br />\n例如單車行山，唱K<br />\n平日會約下飯局，睇下戲，行下街<br />\n起屋企或者扮緊工悶嘅時候都有人陪下吹下水派下膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有感情心事嘅你都可以入黎叫下春<br />\n我地都會有專人安慰你<br />\n不過唔好成日叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想入黎嘅巴絲打好簡單<br />\n先㩒下面條Link 入咗再填form Pm 比admin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAFP-VNfEfC9G9_IWMQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAFP-VNfEfC9G9_IWMQ&d=Hh5C2Wm8JWR9usSbwEl%2Bh7ktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=ffa700c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAFP-VNfEfC9G9_IWMQ</a><br />\n<br />\n另外本谷嚴禁厹，娘娘，5p仔<br />\n請自重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"429455e9af79d1c8ed01d293808aa414ab87ba45","tid":1250393,"uid":2179,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:29:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80b2cd4485bcdb369b8e95345344702a29d017b8","tid":1250393,"uid":2179,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T06:19:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4236e0a24e7e82e04ba737488c78086001b3ae91","tid":1250393,"uid":2179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T08:20:44.000Z